00:53:08,881 --> 00:53:11,449
 [ phone ringing ]

951
00:53:17,890 --> 00:53:21,894
I'm gonna put this money
back into our account.

952
00:53:21,937 --> 00:53:23,765
So you just sit there.

953
00:53:25,898 --> 00:53:27,508
This will take a minute.

954
00:53:30,685 --> 00:53:32,470
Then we'll go home.

955
00:53:36,300 --> 00:53:37,910
[ gasps ]

956
00:53:41,261 --> 00:53:44,351
Woman: 
Jane? Jane Ravenson?

957
00:53:44,395 --> 00:53:45,831
You're Amy's mother.

958
00:53:45,874 --> 00:53:48,529
 Anne. 
Anne Halloran-Gimblet.

959
00:53:48,573 --> 00:53:51,228
- Our daughters 
are in class together.
- Anne Halloran-Gimblet.

960
00:53:51,271 --> 00:53:53,969
I was on that field trip
where you slugged that man

961
00:53:54,013 --> 00:53:55,797
and I always wanted
to call you

962
00:53:55,841 --> 00:53:57,712
and say how terrific
that was.

963
00:53:57,756 --> 00:53:59,497
 I mean, 
all of us mothers,

964
00:53:59,540 --> 00:54:00,628
we were
just standing around

965
00:54:00,672 --> 00:54:02,369
while that pig
pushed our kids

966
00:54:02,413 --> 00:54:04,328
and nobody did anything
but you.

967
00:54:04,371 --> 00:54:07,287
- My dream.
- Anyway, I, uh--

968
00:54:07,331 --> 00:54:09,724
I'm glad I got a chance
to tell you now

969
00:54:09,768 --> 00:54:11,378
that I thought
you were wonderful.

970
00:54:11,422 --> 00:54:13,859
 And I will never 
let six months go by

971
00:54:13,902 --> 00:54:15,513
before I get in touch.

972
00:54:19,038 --> 00:54:21,258
Michael: 
Dr. Gurney's the best 
in his field.

973
00:54:21,301 --> 00:54:24,696
 He's got a private 
psychiatric hospital

974
00:54:24,739 --> 00:54:26,350
 a couple hours 
from here.

975
00:54:26,393 --> 00:54:29,831
I've made an appointment
for us to see him tomorrow

976
00:54:29,875 --> 00:54:31,833
after I get out
of surgery.

977
00:54:33,748 --> 00:54:35,576
 Paula's gonna pack 
some of your things

978
00:54:35,620 --> 00:54:37,099
in case--

979
00:54:38,710 --> 00:54:41,278
in case he wants you
to stay for a couple
of days.

980
00:54:43,367 --> 00:54:45,978
Jane's voice: 
Six months go by.

981
00:54:47,153 --> 00:54:49,851
 Six months go by.

982
00:54:51,853 --> 00:54:55,422
[ stammering ]
Excuse me, ma'am.
I have a return.

983
00:54:59,731 --> 00:55:03,517
I'm sorry, we don't accept
returns with bloodstains.

984
00:55:03,561 --> 00:55:07,216
[ echoes ]
Besides, you bought this
six months ago.

985
00:55:10,829 --> 00:55:13,005
[ echoes ]
Amy?

986
00:55:13,048 --> 00:55:15,660
Amy?

987
00:55:15,703 --> 00:55:17,966
Amy?

988
00:55:18,010 --> 00:55:20,142
Amy?!

