00:55:47,300 --> 00:55:49,389
 Mommy's here.

996
00:55:49,433 --> 00:55:51,435
 Mommy's here.

997
00:55:51,478 --> 00:55:54,220
Mommy's here.
Mommy's here, Amy.

998
00:55:54,263 --> 00:55:56,875
[ stammering ]
Amy!

999
00:55:56,918 --> 00:55:58,877
Amy, no! No!
[ gasps ]

1000
00:55:58,920 --> 00:56:01,401
- [ panting ] No.
- It's okay.

1001
00:56:01,445 --> 00:56:03,795
- No. No.
- Jane, shh.

1002
00:56:03,838 --> 00:56:06,275
- [ cries ]
- Jane, shh.

1003
00:56:06,319 --> 00:56:08,495
It's a dream, Jane.

1004
00:56:08,539 --> 00:56:10,279
Shh, shh.

1005
00:56:15,110 --> 00:56:16,851
Jane's voice: 
Oh, Amy.

1006
00:56:16,895 --> 00:56:18,940
Michael: 
You wanna tell me 
about your dream?

1007
00:56:20,246 --> 00:56:21,552
 Hmm?

